'''Lindsay Dee Lohan''' ({{IPAc-en|ˈ|l|oʊ|h|æ|n}}; Luuliyo 2, 1986<ref name="bbc" />)  waa atariisho Mareykan ah, heesaa, iyo hal-abuure ganacsi.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.lindsaylohanofficial.com/|title=Lindsay Lohan &#124; Home|website=Lindsaylohanofficial.com|access-date=April 20, 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200402232323/http://www.lindsaylohanofficial.com/|archive-date=April 2, 2020|url-status=live}}</ref> Waxay ku dhalatay kuna kortay magaalada New York, Lohan waxaa loo saxiixay [[Ford Models]] markay jirtay seddex sano. Ka dib markii ay si joogto ah uga soo muuqatay taxne telefishinka ''Another World'' iyada oo 10 jir ah, horumarkeedu wuxuu ku yimid filimka [[Walt Disney Pictures]] ''The Parent Trap'' (1998). Guusha filimka ayaa keentay in laga soo muuqdo filimada talefishinada ''[[Life-Size]]'' (2000) iyo ''[[Get a Clue]]'' (2002), iyo wax soo saarka shaashadaha waaweyn ''[[Freaky Friday]]'' (2003) iyo ''[[Confessions of a Teenage Drama Queen]]'' (2004).

Shaqadeedii hore ee Lohan waxay ku guulaysatay xiddignimadeeda caruurnimada, halka filimka ''[[Mean Girls]]'' (2004) uu xaqiijiyay xaaladdeeda [[Idol dhallintii|sanam da'yar]] ah. Kadib markii uu jilay filimka majaajilada ah ee ciyaaraha [[Herbie: Fully Loaded|''Herbie: Fully Loaded'']] (2005), Lohan waxa uu si degdeg ah u noqday mawduuca si weyn looga hadal hayo warbaahinta sababtoo ah halgan shakhsi oo isdaba joog ah iyo dhibaatooyin xagga sharciga ah, iyo sidoo kale tiro badan oo ka mid ah xarumaha baxnaaninta ee isticmaalka mukhaadaraadka.  Muddadani waxa ay lumisay doorar dhawr ah oo ay si weyn u saamaysay shaqadeeda iyo sumcadeeda guud si taban. Intaa ka dib, waxay ka soo muuqatay filimada, sida ''[[A Prairie Home Companion]]'' (2006), ''[[Just My Luck]]''(2006), ''[[Bobby]]'' (2006), [[Chapter 27|''Chapter 27'']] (2007), ''[[Machete]]''(2010), [[Liz & Dick|''Liz & Dick'']] (2012), iyo ''[[The Canyons]]'' (2013).

